   - Improved the double jump functionality.

3. **Improved Anti-Lag System**: 
   - Enhanced performance for smoother gameplay.

## Script Content

```lua
function IsInRealGame()
    local playerY = GetPlayerYPosition()
    if playerY > 0 then
        return true
    end
    return false
end

function AutoJump()
    if IsInRealGame() then
        wait(0.2)  -- Delay added for better double jump
        Jump()
    end
end

